00:16:04,759 --> 00:16:06,519
has brought us so much to look forward to.

288
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,720
It really makes you wonder,

289
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,559
where their journey will finally end.

290
00:16:11,879 --> 00:16:13,039
I just got word

291
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,679
that Yunhua City chose to surrender.

292
00:16:14,919 --> 00:16:17,159
Qiushui City advances directly to the semifinals.

293
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,120
Let's look forward to seeing how these four teams

294
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,679
will perform in the semifinals.

295
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,879
The final four list is out.

296
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,720
The result of the draw is:

297
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:26,879
We're up against

298
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,960
Qiushui City.

299
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:32,480
From a certain perspective,

300
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:34,480
our next match

301
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,720
is no different

302
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:37,080
from the championship game.

303
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,559
Because among the final four,

304
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,840
three of the teams

305
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:44,080
are all from Black Street.

306
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,240
I have to say,

307
00:16:46,919 --> 00:16:48,159
you Black Street folks

308
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,840
are really reliable.

309
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,200
As reliable as we are,

310
00:16:52,639 --> 00:16:54,720
we still almost got taken out by that milk tea.

311
00:16:55,639 --> 00:16:58,720
Don't sweat the small stuff.

312
00:16:58,879 --> 00:17:00,000
In the next match,

313
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:02,120
as long as we take down Qiushui City,

314
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,759
we'll practically be standing

315
00:17:04,759 --> 00:17:05,960
in the champion's spot.

316
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:06,799
What do you say, Su Yang?

317
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,400
Are you confident

318
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:10,359
you can Smash Imperial Capital?

319
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:14,519
Smash Imperial Capital?

320
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,480
That's a bit tough.

321
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:16,960
But I can give it a shot.

322
00:17:17,519 --> 00:17:19,839
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

323
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,160
Tomorrow's match,

324
00:17:21,279 --> 00:17:22,400
you're still leading the charge.

325
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,480
Meeting adjourned.

326
00:17:29,559 --> 00:17:31,079
To Smash Imperial Capital

327
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,240
is actually easy.

328
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,640
But getting away afterwards is the hard part.
